data.description: Charm & Character throughout this well loved Cottage & Barn on Horse-friendly 2+ private acres w/ year round mountain views minutes to Lake James amenities & downtown Morganton shopping & festivities. Have your small farm or vacation getaway w/ level RV parking & 220 amp hookup. Live edge wood sided home has an efficient one level open floorplan with an abundance of natural light. Original Hardwood & new vinyl plank flooring, new replacement windows, gas Fireplace in LR & tankless hot water heater. Open foyer entrance. Two gracious bedrooms and full bathroom with convenient Laundry. Kitchen with breakfast bar & dining area. Walk in pantry. Covered front screened deck and side open deck overlooking the back/side yard. Separate Barn/Stable for farm animals & storage. Mature landscaping, Blueberry bushes, Concord grape vines, Apple trees & plenty of room to garden. up. Multiple outbuildings, Greenhouse, Chicken coop & lean too. Prettier in Person! Easy to show. Shown by Appointment.
